text=!! Office Management Board%0a%0a# %25outline%25 Composition%0a## The Office Management Board shall consist of the following:%0a### the Office Manager, who is the chair of the Board;%0a### the Novelties Director%0a### any persons appointed to the Board by the chair or by the Vice-President, Activities and Services; and%0a### the Vice-President, Finances.%0a## The Vice-President, Activities and Services, will also be an ex-officio member of the Board.%0a%0a# Powers & Duties%0a## The Office Management Board shall be charged with the following duties:%0a### maintaining order and general security of the Society office;%0a### arranging office hours;%0a### selling of all items from the Society office;%0a### distributing lockers and removing the lock and contents of illegally taken lockers;%0a### general maintenance of the photocopiers;%0a### ordering and maintaining an adequate stock of office supplies;%0a### training all new office workers; and%0a### reporting to Council on the status of the Office Management Board.%0a%0a# Office Manager%0a## The Office Manager shall be appointed by, shall report to, and shall be responsible to the Vice-President, Activities and Services.%0a
